# Cursor Rules for DDS Validation Project

## MCP Configuration
You can use the following MCP servers with this project:

### MIRO MCP
To use MIRO MCP, you need to:
1. Install the MIRO MCP server
2. Configure it in your Cursor settings
3. Use it through the chat interface

### Available MCP Commands
- Create boards
- Add elements to boards
- Manage team access
- Export boards
- Real-time collaboration features

## Project Guidelines
- Work within the 'app' folder structure
- Follow modern code style and architecture
- Prioritize reusable components
- Maintain full responsiveness
- Use structured Design System with light/dark themes 